
# codex cli linux mint xfce
# Official method is by using Node.js + npm
# Following steps are without npm + nodejs

website             :       https://github.com/openai/codex/
Releases            :       https://github.com/openai/codex/releases/latest
installed version   :       rust-v0.121.0


download file named :       codex-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz

un pack the file    :       tar -xzf codex-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz 

rename the file     :       mv codex-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl codex

Make it executable  :       chmod +x codex

Move to system PATH :       sudo mv codex /usr/local/bin/

Verify installation :       codex --version

Login/setup         :       codex login